{"tid":1748844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"說服唔到奶奶投黃色議員，唯有出呢招！","createTime":"2019-11-24T00:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T00:45:12.000Z","uid":292490,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"60dfc634bb5f02291470573d81e82f577412e5db","tid":1748844,"uid":292490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T00:18:33.000Z","msg":"噚晚發咗個咁嘅夢<br />\n<br />\n話說我奶奶係唔識分黃同藍，只係覺得佢應該投票俾成日喺度幫佢哋修橋補路同送禮物嘅議員，用咗好多方法解釋佢聽叫佢唔好投民賤聯，跟住佢話好啦，我唔投民賤聯啦，我唔投佢佢都應該唔知嘅，個議員問我說話投咗佢啦。<br />\n<br />\n咁我就好開心啦，以為成功，跟住我老公話唔好信佢，佢估佢會偷偷哋去投，然後我老公星期六下晝就去攞咗佢張身分證話要幫佢搞伸請津貼嗰d嘢，佢d生果金呀，乜津貼物津貼都係我幫佢伸請嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住夜晚佢個女就whatsapp問我哋係哋攞咗佢阿媽張身分證，佢阿媽話約咗人星期日去投票，話我哋攞咗佢張身分證，但佢又唔敢問個仔攞返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩有收咗佢張証，唔係就蝕一票！<br />\n<br />\n大家記得照顧好身邊嘅長者呀！<br />\n<br />\n起身去投票啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c943d5cf5140d66c24ee323b2a44029a0c348248","tid":1748844,"uid":207977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T00:20:27.000Z","msg":"做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d42c0bc8706332a2b4b2bcdde42be986bfb4d8","tid":1748844,"uid":205684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T00:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O63JBah.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO63JBah.jpg&h=600699c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b6b773fb09c5b142d01db3885652a458166c146","tid":1748844,"uid":23190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T00:22:27.000Z","msg":"以前試過回鄉證都投得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213a1cfb9f28cf93a02ec7b96affc2f4e1e2a05e","tid":1748844,"uid":55891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T00:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365e1868486eb4